      </div>
  
    
      <div class="historia-texto">
        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>
          In <strong>El Rinc√≥n del Repostero</strong>,our story begins with a lit oven and a clear vision: to take the art of pastry making to another level. We were born from a passion for authentic flavors, delicate aesthetics and tradition passed down from generation to generation.
